{
  "arquivo": "ed05_02_01",
  "total": 85,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "",
      "texto_en": "Five years later%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Welcome%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Oh, it's you guys.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Ichika, welcome back!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "It's been a while.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Long time no see, you three.\\nIt's good to see you looking well.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "And I see the shop is obviously bursting at the seams with customers. ",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, yeah, and here I thought you were better at those sarcastic American-style jokes. ",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Well, come on, I thought one of you\\nwould at least come pick me up%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "I never expected the bride herself to come meet me.\\nI was pretty surprised.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Ahaha...\\nI told Itsuki not to go by herself,\\nbut she didn't listen.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Well, of course.\\nShe came all the way back from America just for me.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Itsuki-chan is still as serious or rather,\\nconscientious as ever.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "She finally got rid of her stiff way of talking,\\nbut her personality hasn't changed.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "But isn't it better for a teacher to be serious?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Being too serious might not be good either.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Well, being too sweet is also bad, right?\\nIt seems difficult to strike a balance.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "So? Are you doing well as a teacher?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Don't worry, I'm doing well,\\nand I'm having a lot of fun now.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Fun?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Hmm, for example,\\nthinking about what kind of lessons to teach.\\nAlthough, I'm still experimenting with it.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "I'm happy when I gradually change the way I teach\\nand get better reactions from the students.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Besides, all my students are good kids.\\nThe other day, they surprised me\\nwith a wedding celebration.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I see, it seems to be going well.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "There are many difficult things too.\\nBut overall, it's very fulfilling.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "I'd like to take your class, Itsuki.\\nHow about doing it here?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "No! This isn't a cram school.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "The regulars who just started coming here\\nwould be surprised.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Oh, you have regulars now too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Yes. We're on the right track for now.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "We have to do our best for our father-in-law,\\nwho lent us this place too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Yes, let's both do our best.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "You being so dedicated to work, Itsuki,\\nnow I'm worried about your new life with Fu-kun.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Why is that?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "If you only pay attention to your students,\\nhe might get sulky, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Futaro gets surprisingly lonely,\\ndespite looking the way he does.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "He might say something like,",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "'Which one is more important to you?\\nMe or your students?!'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "I don't think he would say something like that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "You never knooow?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Well, if that happens,\\nI'll make sure to support him at home.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Oh-ho?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Mmmm.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Huh? Why that reaction?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Support him at home, you said.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "I see.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "I-it's not like I said it\\nwith any weird intentions, you know?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Then, how do you plan to support him?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "A-anyway! We should go to the venue soon!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "That's right, we have preparations to make.\\nAlso, my makeup artist is coming too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Are you really going to do it?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Of course. Itsuki's pretty excited herself.\\nWe'll have to have Fu-kun confirm it for us.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "But, before that, let's take care of this first.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Ichika.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "I wore it here.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "The one I kept\\nended up staying in storage.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "This is our wedding gift to you, Itsuki.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "It's Mom's heirloom earrings.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "One, two, three%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "personagem": "All 4",
      "texto_en": "Itsuki, congratulations on getting married!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Thank you.\\nI'll cherish them.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 63,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "No, you should put them on right now.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 64,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, you have to wear them for today's ceremony!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 66,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "R-right, that's true, it's going to happen.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 67,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I'll pierce your ears. Come over here.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 68,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Um, well, about that...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 69,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Actually, I'm still thinking if it's okay\\nto get my ears pierced.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 70,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "You see, I'm a teacher, so I have to\\nbe a good role model for my students%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 71,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Saying that kind of thing, you're just scared, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 72,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Ooh... That's...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 73,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Bulls-eye.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 74,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Ooohh...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 75,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Besides, there are a few colleagues of yours\\nwho have their ears pierced, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 76,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "A few.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 77,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Then it's not a problem, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 78,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "B-but...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 79,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "It's okay, I'll be gentle with you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 80,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Yes, that's right, I'll support you as well.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 81,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "WAA?!\\nYotsuba, let go of me!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 82,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "The pain only lasts for a moment.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 83,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Okay, here we gooo!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 84,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "HYEEEEEEE?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}